Description: IBus input method engine for Chinese (Pinyin, Wubi, Wbpy, ASR)
 TUX IM is a Python-based IBus engine that provides:
  * Pinyin phonetic input
  * Wubi 86 stroke input
  * Wbpy (automatic mixed Wubi + Pinyin)
  * ASR voice input via cloud API
 .
 It uses RIME-format dictionaries and integrates with the IBus framework
 on Linux desktops.
